{"tid":923364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句話惹惱天下同志　同志交友軟體總監怪翻譯","createTime":"2018-12-01T07:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T07:56:11.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d004c0dad9018cf6793a6b221a3d3d2efbf0f241","tid":923364,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T07:40:25.000Z","msg":"以同志為對象的交友平台總監，竟然發表反同言論？全球最大同志交友平台Grindr的台裔總監陳俊仰（Scott Chen）<br />\n在臉書的一段貼文，「婚姻是一男一女的神聖結合」，遭Grindr內部網站揭露，全球同志社群譁然。<br />\n《紐約時報》今天報導，Grindr內部消息指出，陳俊仰26日在個人臉書頁面上轉貼連結，文章是一篇談及宏達電集團董事長王雪紅資助反同組織的行為。陳俊仰在這段貼文下面留言，表示「有人覺得婚姻是一男一女的神聖結合，我也覺得是，但這是你家的事」。<br />\n陳俊仰的言論被Grindr旗下的網站「Into」報導後在社群網路上遭瘋傳，網友認為這是恐同言論，眾多Grindr用戶表示不滿。陳俊仰辯稱自己的言論被臉書自動翻譯成英文後讓人誤解，他隨後貼文澄清自己支持同性婚姻，「關於覺得婚姻是一男一女的神聖結合，只是根據我個人經驗」。<br />\nGrindr總部位於美國加州，自2009年推出至今已成為全球最受歡迎的同志手機交友軟體，在全球196個國家共有約380萬用戶。中國的遊戲開發商崑崙萬維集團今年1月砸1.52億美元100%收購Grindr後，原創辦人西姆凱（Joel Simkhai）卸下總監職位，陳俊仰當時接任為技術長、並於8月升為總監。<br />\n據《紐約時報》報導，Grindr官方對此事件沒有回應。（許可／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181130/640_69119540c5ff65b5b2be9421042ab14b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181130%2F640_69119540c5ff65b5b2be9421042ab14b.jpg&h=ffa269a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181130/640_a3af7c82437e8f7bdae89c00f372b488.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181130%2F640_a3af7c82437e8f7bdae89c00f372b488.jpg&h=166cc231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181130/1476351/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181130%2F1476351%2F&d=ZNf2MwaxqR1LA9olbv5jbDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=bc173064\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181130%2F1476351%2F&h=d20618e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181130/1476351/</a>"},{"pid":"d93958c00b999784b213dfda46cfb13c47fe86a0","tid":923364,"uid":193364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T07:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班塔利班"},{"pid":"1950c2c70572c97a64c5410521bec5ba31c3ab2c","tid":923364,"uid":170229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T07:46:26.000Z","msg":"西方左膠不意外<br />\ncontext wfc"},{"pid":"1ee11dfda4312cc2bf9061bafa15ea1da6b3fb5e","tid":923364,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T07:47:19.000Z","msg":"個心又碎晒<br />\n係咪想個個男同男、女同女，全世界所有人都唔生仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86394dfd00b3bc90c6e0ad8b160d95e4b1c9fa3","tid":923364,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T07:56:11.000Z","msg":"下一次又到邊件玻璃心呀<br />\n依家啲人吓吓都一句話惹惱_______<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}